snippet.title: Electric Fancave Ep. 102 [w/ Seth Millstein!]
snippet.description:
Tonight's topics include:

- Johnny Depp, Amber Heard, and celebrities defending other celebrities accused of domestic violence 
- Captain America's villainous turn
- Dan Aykroyd's controversial Ghostbusters love
- Does Finding Dory have the first Disney/Pixar lesbian couple?
- Kit Harington thinks Hollywood is sexist against men

All this and more LIVE @8pm PT/11pm ET. Hop in and comment along!
